{"tid":1229274,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG]森太軟吹水玩樂谷","createTime":"2019-06-16T01:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T11:59:36.000Z","uid":83952,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"65e9dfe8d704323a409f6cc41515560954e3c8f9","tid":1229274,"uid":83952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:09:22.000Z","msg":"簡介：<br />\n各位好，若果你搵緊行山腳 / 露營腳 / 觀星腳等等，不妨考慮加入本谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時本谷得兩個「有丁絲打」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋兩個都係活躍份子，主力行山+露營，我哋露營裝備都叫齊，若果你有興趣露營的話不妨入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我尋晚先去完大尾篤影星，嚟緊下星期六又準備去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我熱到死都會想行下山嘅癡線山友嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不論有丁冇丁巴絲打都歡迎，廢青定廢老都入得嚟<br />\n<br />\n本谷資訊<br />\n~歡迎加入本谷~<br />\n本谷宗旨： 開開心心一班人玩，唔開心就拎出嚟呻下<br />\n主力舉辦行山/露營/觀星/攝影/飯局/吹水酒局等等<br />\n歡迎各位參與我哋嘅活動<br />\n本谷規矩：<br />\n1. 尊重他人<br />\n2. J圖唔貼得<br />\n本谷唔介意同其他谷聯合活動，不過要問清楚對方是否容許；同時鼓勵各位自行舉辦活動<br />\n有問題PM ADMIN就可以<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FirjQBZCrhOXio3Btsmweg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFirjQBZCrhOXio3Btsmweg&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhmipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=f4cf0966\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FirjQBZCrhOXio3Btsmweg</a>"},{"pid":"c7446e756